This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it presents a new image dataset and baseline results for various machine learning tasks. It may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories as it discusses machine learning tasks and exports the dataset in a machine learning friendly format. Additionally, it may belong to the cryptography and security (cs.CR) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories as it mentions transparency and standardization of dataset information.
